name: Forma Naturalis - 05
description: Element of casualness, of spontaneity, as the distinctive (or unifying) element between computer, nature, according to which evolutionary mechanisms cannot be predicted from their constituent elements and it is often impossible to reconstruct them, starting from their visible manifestations. Inspired by abstract form, kunstformen der natur, minimal aesthetic, and natural phenomena. This piece created by @vvaxx_ (Instagram / Twitter)
